description.displayText: Delia was a very dedicated employee when she worked for me. She took care of my three children in the morning and also performed housekeeping duties like cleaning, vacuuming and laundry. She's very responsible and punctual as well as providing regular updates on the kids throughout the day when I needed it. I highly recommend her she's a trustful person.
